description: Welcome to this beautifully upgraded upstairs corner unit in the desirable Canyon Bluffs community of Mira Mesa, San Diego. This bright and airy 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo includes a spacious loft, vaulted ceilings, and abundant natural light. The upgraded kitchen features upgraded cabinetry, pendant lights, stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. The primary bedroom showcases a stylish wood accent wall. The living room fireplace has been refreshed with a contemporary/industrial look.  Enjoy the convenience of a newer washer, dryer, and hot water heater, plus ample storage with a large attic, patio closet, and carport storage closet. Community amenities include a pool and spa, offering resort-style living in a prime location.  Nearby you will find various hiking trails, restaurants and the 5 Freeway.
